                @*Phone:
                
                iPhone 4 wallpaper size – 640×960
                iPhone 5 wallpaper size – 640×1136
                Samsung/HTC/LG – 480×800
                Samsung/HTC/LG/Sony – 720×1280
                HTC/Motorola – 540×960
                Sony/Motorola – 480×854*@

            </div>
        </form>
    </fieldset>

